{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"73b12cc83c","title":"给李×的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"54bdc627a9","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":20,"articleId":"73b12cc83c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949.10-1957.12）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a1537749eb","type":"paragraph","text":"对季×实践论解说的两处修改","index":0,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"9cbf87685b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五二年三月）","index":1,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"58ae1a7f30","type":"paragraph","text":"、中国人民那时还不知道应当把外国的政府和人民、餐本家和工人、地主和农民加以区别，我们应当反对使署中国的外国地主餐本家和政府官员，他何是帝国主义，而在宣傅上争取外国的人民，并不是一切外国人都是坏人，都要排斤。这即是那时的中国人还·.","index":2,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"013f2e53c4","type":"paragraph","text":"二、虽然辛支革命实际上起了反对帝国主义的作用，因为推翻了帝国主义的走狗一满清政府，当然就带有反帝的作用，因而引起了帝国主义对于辛支革命的不满，不帮助孙中山而帮助袁世号，但是当时的革命党人的主观上并没有密这一点，而韶为.....","index":3,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"61e0cfad3c","type":"paragraph","text":"给李×的一封信","index":4,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"2a832302b1","type":"paragraph","text":"一封信××兄：","index":5,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"dbab0afc6f","type":"paragraph","text":"两次来信及附来实践融解证第二部分，均收到了。翻翻你！解证的第一部分也在刊物上看到了。这个解酚极好，对于用通俗的言帮宣傅唯物有很大的作用。待你的第三部分写完并发表之后，应当出-一单行本，以广流傅。第二部分中融帝国主义和教条主义、经验主义的那两真上有--点小的修改，请加，如已发表，请在印单行本时修改好了。","index":6,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"788a535ec7","type":"paragraph","text":"关于辩唯物融的通俗宣傅，过去做得太少，而不满足广大工作干部和青年学生的追切需要，希望你多多写些文章","index":7,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"74b42f79f1","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":8,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"8865c9dcd9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛澡东","index":9,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"14b141e49a","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年三月二十日实践融中将太平天国放在挑外主义一起设不委，出选集时，拟加修改，此处暂仍回原。","index":10,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"cf239e7ca4","type":"paragraph","text":"我们也应当会办经济","index":11,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"a905d080bd","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五二年七月）","index":12,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"},{"id":"b8515a3f16","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不但应敲会办政治，会办军事，会办党务，会办文化，我们也应当会办经济，如果我们样样能干，惟独经济无能，那我们就是一批无用之人，就要被政人打倒，就要陷子灭。","index":13,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c"}],"page":{"id":"b5959694e3","publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"73b12cc83c","start":30,"end":30}}}},"__N_SSG":true}